ANC secretary-general Gwede Mantashe has called for action to be taken against the commissioner of police for lying about the swimming pool at Nkandla by describing it as a fire pool.Mantashe was speaking at an ANC press conference in Joburg this morning following the release of the Public Protector s report on upgrades of more than R200 million at the president s private home.He did not mention national police commissioner Riah Phiyega by name.The real Zumaville24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.